<p>This is my <a href="https://nownownow.com/about">now</a> page. Inspired by my colleagues <a href="https://rknight.me/now/">Robb</a> and <a href="https://zoeaubert.me/now/">Zoe</a>. The purpose of this page is to share what I'm currently doing in my life.</p>

<h2>What am I up to currently?</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Living near Portsmouth with my wife and daughter</li>
    <li>Working at Radweb on all things software and infrastructure</li>
    <li>Driving our BMW 530e G30 and loving every trip</li>
    <li>Losing weight through exercise, mostly running and cycling</li>
</ul>

<h2>How is my weight loss going?</h2>

<p>Since January 2023 I've lost {{ health.weightLoss }}kg through diet and exercise. <a href="https://www.secondnature.io/">Second Nature</a> and <a href="https://www.parkrun.org.uk/parkrunner/8212898/">Parkrun</a> have been a huge help for my weight loss success, that, and wanting to provide the best life for my newborn daughter.</p>

<p>I'm currently trying to add 10 minutes of stretching and 20 minutes of strength training into my daily routing. As well as adding two 5k runs during my working week. Once the days are longer I will likely introduce daily walks, and weekly cycling as I done last year.</p>

